{
  "text": "Including the results of previous reports [CITATION_1] , the range of BF Ab over the three different days was 1153-4401 ml/ min in the 60 participants. Furthermore, the mean value of BF Ab was 2630 \u00b1 649 ml/min in 18 of the participants (age range, 20-38 years) in the previous reports [CITATION_2] .",
